
### Задачи
GET http://localhost:38109/zp/tasks

### Настройки задачи
GET http://localhost:38109/zp/settings-xml?task_id=92ca9a3d-a8dc-4690-9ecc-2e34265f8c76


### Команды pending
GET http://localhost:10993/zp/commands?status=pending

### Создать команду
POST http://localhost:10993/zp/commands
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "task_id": "123",
  "action": "start",
  "payload": ""
}

### PM Bridge — пометить выполненной
POST http://localhost:10993/zp/commands/done
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "uuid-сюда",
  "result": "ok",
  "status": "done"
}